headline: D&H Fortinet Security Partnership Expansion Might Change The Case For Investing In Fortinet (FTNT)
summary: D&H recently announced a major partnership integrating Fortinet’s full security suite into its Advanced Solutions+ ecosystem for U.S. channel partners, alongside the launch of the FWD enablement program offering structured training, workshops, and dedicated Fortinet expertise. This collaboration materially deepens Fortinet’s indirect distribution reach by equipping VARs, MSPs, MSSPs, and other partners to design and manage end-to-end security solutions built on Fortinet technology. headline: Will Fortinet (FTNT) Beat Estimates Again in Its Next Earnings Report?
